args: Something on your mind, Siren?\nYou look awfully pensive.
Oh, hey, Mym.\nSo, here's the sitch...
Is that all? I've got you covered, hon.\nHere, come with me!
Daaarling! Pop star season is here!
Yep. Siren's planning to put on a big show\nwith some of her musically inclined pals!
But there's ONE thing we're still missing.\nCan you guess what that might be?
Here's a hint: you know how Siren and\nthe others are all top-tier performers?
The thing is, they're SO good that their\nshows can be a little intimidating for\nfirst-timers.
What we really need is an act that'll\ncapture the heart of the average person.
And that's where you come in, darling!
We want you to form a brand-new boy\nband and knock everyone's socks clean off!
You'd be doing your girl Siren SUCH a\nsolid. Pretty please?
You want me to be a pop star?\nI mean, I do want to help you, but...\nI don't know if I'm cut out for that.
His Highness has enough duties as it is.\nI hardly think it appropriate to—
(C'mon, don't you wanna see my darling\nflashing that gorgeous smile your way?\nOr maybe even—gasp—WINKING at you?!)
I know, right? So just play along!
Your Highness! I believe there is merit\nin giving this ＂pop star＂ venture a try.
Wait, really?\nWhat made you change your mind?
Your smile brings hope and courage to the\ncitizens of this land.
This is something only you can do.\nWe'll do everything we can to support\nyou, so please! The world needs you!
Well? Are you in? Sounds like you're in!
Well, okay... If you really think\nI'm the right man for the job.
Yippee! Next order of business is\nto fill out the rest of the group.
One order of meat, comin' right up!
Oh, c'mon! You didn't even try it!

It sure is! That takes care of the
whole lineup. This summer, the
lucky gents who get to stand on
stage with {player_name} are...
I'd totally fit in with these guys! I mean,\nI've got the swimsuit 'n everything!
Well... You do have a certain Ranzal-y\nappeal. And you DID grill for us...
But you're just not boy-band material!
Moving on... I'm sure all you boys are\ngonna sparkle out there. Congratulations\non your pop star debut!
Wait. What? Who's a pop star?
Uh, you? Duh-doy. That's what you just\nauditioned for, remember?
I...did? Wait, you mean when you forcibly\ndragged me here and told me to, and I\nquote, ＂show off them skillz＂?
I see... So that was an audition.\nI too underwent such an ordeal.
Such underhanded techniques.\nAnd for something as pointless as a\nboy band? I don't have time for this.
You guys sure this is gonna work out okay?
All right, everybody, eyes on me! Your new\nboy band will be called...drumroll please...
Oh, come on! We worked really\nhard on this, you jerk!
No need to blow your top, Mym.\nWe've got our soon-to-be stars wrangled\ntogether, so let's just dooo thiiis thaaang!
Burning up the summer stage,\nit's the SUMMER SIZZLERS!\nThey're so hot, they'll melt your heart!
(I have a feeling we're in for\none memorable summer...)
